{"tid":2117883,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"21名中國人偷渡去越南，因中國工廠倒閉失業，期望去越南搵工做","createTime":"2020-07-21T06:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T07:59:23.000Z","uid":48040,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1ee551910328e1da638215cd6f2ab6aa3c54b6","tid":2117883,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:49:04.000Z","msg":"越南廣南省奠磐市社（Điện B&agrave;n）執法人員日前檢查當地一處居民區時發現，有一批中國人在此非法居留。這些非法入境者共21人，他們試圖逃跑，不過此後均被拘捕。這些非法入境者被執法人員送往三歧市（Tam Ky）隔離。<br />\n網上傳聞指，這21名中國人因中國工廠倒閉失業，期望去越南搵工做。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1285465987458818049?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1285465987458818049%3Fs%3D20&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=90ebd920\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1285465987458818049%3Fs%3D20&h=79d375ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1285465987458818049?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"f63b9c226f01886e0f7e7f2566e5d1485ac7836d","tid":2117883,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"賣淫咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec6f857f7c6e39958581294f7bf63ff24444479","tid":2117883,"uid":110562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:57:08.000Z","msg":"下 叛國罪WO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fa3387394b81efac800c10efc4a64151392da9","tid":2117883,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"偷渡去越南？一帶一路，唔係可以去義大利、德國發展事業嗎，親～"},{"pid":"2f8ca078d0ba697279322cca46e97e1c3f2cfe23","tid":2117883,"uid":5490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:00:30.000Z","msg":"違反港區國安法"},{"pid":"1185d0bdf97b6e0400c4cc54b5adfed4407984c7","tid":2117883,"uid":287269,"like":0,"dislike"